			<td valign="top">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Once you're into all-ways scrolling territory there's no real maximum map size. The real problem is just how much space the map data takes up in your ROM; if you have some sort of simple repetitive rubber-stamp room system you might get very large indeed.<br /><br />You might want to poke around at VGMaps: <a href="http://vgmaps.com/Atlas/index.htm#NES" class="postlink">http://vgmaps.com/Atlas/index.htm#NES</a></div>

